Color (in alcohol). Dorsal scutum background Deep Orange Yellow (
69
) with darker shading especially in lateral areas and carapace. Smaller granules of scutum and main paramedian tubercles of area III are considerably darker. Larger rounded tubercles of lateral area only slightly lighter than background. Articular membranes white. Chelicerae and pedipalps background Strong Yellow (
84
